Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:40.35,Kingdom-ED-Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\k11}{\K76}壊{\k13}れ{\K61}そう{\K55}な{\k16}{\K115}心{\k22} {\K79}紡{\k25}ぐ{\K45}よう{\K64}に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:40.35,Kingdom-ED-English,,0,0,0,,To weave together my breaking heart
